Let me analyze the task and provide a detailed solution:

1. Analysis of Target Image:
- Total Blocks: 9 blocks
- Layers: 3 layers
- Colors: Green, Yellow, Blue, Red, Orange
- Structure: Complex architectural design with arched openings

2. Required Blocks from Dictionary:
- Green vertical block (index 7)
- Yellow horizontal block (index 9)
- Blue cube blocks (index 4, used twice)
- Red arch blocks (index 1)
- Orange cylindrical blocks (index 10, used twice)
- Orange triangular roof blocks (index 15)

3. Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 7 (green vertical block)
    Step2: Move block with index 9 (yellow horizontal block) on top of green block
    Step3: Move block with index 10 (orange cylinder) on yellow block
    Step4: Move another block with index 10 (orange cylinder) next to first cylinder
    Step5: Move block with index 9 (yellow horizontal block) in front of cylinders
    Step6: Move block with index 1 (red arch) over yellow block
    Step7: Move block with index 4 (blue cube) under red arch
    Step8: Move another block with index 4 (blue cube) next to first blue cube
    Step9: Move block with index 1 (red arch) over blue cubes
    Step10: Move block with index 15 (orange triangular roof) on top of red arch
}
